casebody.data:
Tuesday, March 14, 1995

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

94-2161. No. L-92-362. Toledo Blank, Inc. v. Pioneer Steel Serv. Co. Lucas County,

This cause is pending before the court on the certification of conflict by the Court of Appeals for Lucas County. Upon consideration of the joint application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application be, and the same is hereby, granted, effective March 13, 1995.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
